# Ignore everything by default.
*

# Keep Keil project configuration visible to Git.
!*.uvprojx
!Project.uvprojx

# Keep source directories visible to Git.
!Hardware/
!User/
!System/
!Control/
!App/
!Start/
!Library/

# Track all Hardware and System sources.
!Hardware/**
!System/**

# Track the control module introduced by staged refactors.
!Control/**
!App/**
!Start/**
!Library/**

# Track the current application entry.
!User/main.c
!User/stm32f10x_conf.h
!User/stm32f10x_it.c
!User/stm32f10x_it.h

# Track this ignore file.
!.gitignore
!AGENTS.md
